    "Ritchie left the Albright Museum in 1949, replaced by Edgar Schenck, to head the department of painting and sculpture at the Museum of Modern Art, New York, succeeding <a href=\"/dharnoncourtr\">Ren\u00e9 d'Harnoncourt</a> who had now become the MoMA's director.": [],
    "In 1957 accepted an appointment to head the Yale University Art Gallery, replacing Lamont Moore.": [],
